  <name>PixelBatch</name>
  <summary>Batch Image Optimization Tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>PixelBatch is a powerful batch image optimization application that helps you reduce file sizes while maintaining quality. Perfect for web developers, photographers, and content creators.</p>
    <p>Key features of PixelBatch:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-format support: JPEG, PNG, GIF, and SVG optimization</li>
      <li>Professional optimizers: jpegoptim for JPEG, pngquant for PNG, gifsicle for GIF, and SVGO for SVG</li>
      <li>Batch processing: Optimize hundreds of images at once</li>
      <li>Concurrent processing: Multi-threaded optimization for speed</li>
      <li>Lossless and lossy compression: Choose your quality vs size trade-off</li>
      <li>Real-time statistics: See file size reduction as you work</li>
      <li>Format-specific settings: Fine-tune optimization for each image type</li>
      <li>Dark and light themes: Qt Creator-inspired professional interface</li>
      <li>Drag and drop: Simple, intuitive workflow</li>
      <li>Re-processing support: Test different settings easily</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
